127176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"492b4d019b5ae551622da639d9d0fa23b57fdfd4","tid":1758284,"uid":238415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實馬拉人支唔支持我覺得無咩所謂<br />\n我係唔明一班移左民或者所謂華人兼唔係既得利益者既人<br />\n日日係度一個中國自high打飛機係為左乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"就係因為佢地移咗民，係馬拉作為少數民族被異族欺壓過，但又未去到要經歷好似印尼柬埔寨嘅悲劇，同埋馬拉係東南亞入面共產勢力影響相對少嘅國家，所以佢地冇感受過中共嘅無情，更冇咩點受過共產黨嘅欺壓，反而睇到中國風光嘅表面，因為中共嘅強大而得到正面嘅影響<br />\n<br />\n仲有黃明志之前提過另一個原因，就係馬拉老華人入面有好多都好憎國民黨/民國，所以對於打敗國民黨嘅共產黨產生好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14dc7405f4a10d95870c188d0fe33acb81d5caaf","tid":1758284,"uid":98961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"理性到佢地馬拉本來都禁佢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個有骨氣有才華既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ador